conversation.question: what is avalanche method?
conversation.answer: Based on the book "Debt-Free to Financial Freedom," the avalanche method prioritizes paying off debts with the highest interest rates first. This minimizes the total interest paid over time. Continue making minimum payments on all debts but allocate extra funds to the high-interest debt. (Source: Chapter 4)
